{"id":10673,"date":"2024-01-12T13:09:07","date_gmt":"2024-01-12T06:09:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10673"},"modified":"2024-01-12T13:09:07","modified_gmt":"2024-01-12T06:09:07","slug":"co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y kh\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh <\/span>c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. V\u1eady h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Vinhomeland<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u01b0u v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00ec nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Khi ch\u1ecdn mua ho\u1eb7c thu\u00ea c\u0103n h\u1ed9, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y b\u1edfi v\u00ec:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n: C\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian khi di chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf xa ho\u1eb7c \u1edf t\u1ea7ng cao.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c: V\u1ecb tr\u00ed g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y l\u00e0m cho vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c, mua s\u1eafm hay chuy\u1ec3n nh\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m: C\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch nh\u01b0 b\u00e3i \u0111\u1ed7 xe, ph\u00f2ng gym, h\u1ed3 b\u01a1i, gi\u00fap c\u01b0 d\u00e2n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ec7n nghi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan t\u1ed1t: C\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5, ban c\u00f4ng g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9 xa thang m\u00e1y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">An to\u00e0n v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p: Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7n s\u01a1 t\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1, c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y gi\u00fap c\u01b0 d\u00e2n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn thang tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n: Th\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng \u1edf xa thang m\u00e1y, \u0111\u00f4i khi gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ebfn 5-10% t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10675\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10675\" class=\"wp-image-10675 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-1.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10675\" class=\"wp-image-10675 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-1.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10675\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m khi ch\u1ecdn mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch tr\u00ean, b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf khi mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y, v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c quan tr\u1ecdng m\u00e0 c\u01b0 d\u00e2n \u1edf nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n. Thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y d\u00e0i, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u00e2m thanh kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ti\u1ebfng c\u1eeda \u0111\u00f3ng, ti\u1ebfng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a thang m\u00e1y v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t vi\u1ec7c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 gi\u1ea3m \u1ed3n v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a thang m\u00e1y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00e1ch \u00e2m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong c\u00e1c khu v\u1ef1c l\u00e2n c\u1eadn thang m\u00e1y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10676\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10676\" class=\"wp-image-10676 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-2.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10676\" class=\"wp-image-10676 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-2.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10676\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n khi s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y<\/p><\/div>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng gian ri\u00eang t\u01b0. C\u01b0 d\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1eeda c\u0103n h\u1ed9 n\u1eb1m ngay khu v\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4i khi bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 can thi\u1ec7p t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i l\u1ea1i ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb c\u01b0 d\u00e2n kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 phi\u1ec1n to\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ri\u00eang t\u01b0 nh\u01b0 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda, m\u00e0n c\u1eeda ch\u1eafn, ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ea3m ri\u00eang t\u01b0<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10677\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10677\" class=\"wp-image-10677 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-3.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10677\" class=\"wp-image-10677 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-3.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10677\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng khi mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y<\/p><\/div>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 an to\u00e0n<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn an ninh. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01b0 d\u00e2n sinh s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c thang m\u00e1y, c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ee5 t\u1eadp \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u01b0 d\u00e2n trong t\u00f2a nh\u00e0, t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh thang m\u00e1y, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u01b0 d\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10678\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10678\" class=\"wp-image-10678 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-4.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10678\" class=\"wp-image-10678 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-4.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10678\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n khi s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y<\/p><\/div>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed h\u1eb9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf trong c\u0103n h\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10679\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10679\" class=\"wp-image-10679 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-5.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10679\" class=\"wp-image-10679 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-5.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10679\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">V\u1eady c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p phi\u1ec1n to\u00e1i t\u1eeb ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n c\u1ee7a thang m\u00e1y, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t v\u00ec n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 &#8220;\u0111\u1eb9p&#8221; h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfu ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 mua nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 &#8220;\u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n,&#8221; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem x\u00e9t vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c khu chung c\u01b0 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi t\u00fai ti\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu gi\u00e1 mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thanh to\u00e1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n t\u1eeb thang m\u00e1y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn c\u0103n h\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u1ea3 quan. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 mua th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 b\u00e1n v\u00ec \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n mua ch\u00fang.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10680\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10680\" class=\"wp-image-10680 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-6.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10680\" class=\"wp-image-10680 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-6.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 mua th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n, nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 b\u00e1n v\u00ec \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n mua ch\u00fang.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u0103n h\u1ed9 trong chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 phong th\u1ee7y v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Khi mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 \u1edf g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c thang m\u00e1y. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1eddng \u00e2m c\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec thang m\u00e1y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n thang m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 s\u1ef1 ri\u00eang t\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf ch\u1ecdn c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c r\u00e1c ho\u1eb7c n\u01a1i x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u00f9i h\u00f4i v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4n tr\u00f9ng g\u00e2y phi\u1ec1n to\u00e1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p, gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m nhanh ch\u00f3ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng t\u1eeb 7 \u0111\u1ebfn 12 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t l\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed &#8220;\u0111\u1eb9p&#8221; nh\u1ea5t. C\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao, t\u1ea1o thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10681\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10681\" class=\"wp-image-10681 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-7.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/474;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10681\" class=\"wp-image-10681 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may-7.jpg\" alt=\"c\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y\" width=\"800\" height=\"474\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10681\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p, gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t hi\u1ec3m nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/co-nen-mua-chung-cu-gan-thang-may\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>C\u00f3 n\u00ean mua chung c\u01b0 g\u1ea7n thang m\u00e1y<\/b><\/a> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">hay kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t nhu c\u1ea7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1ea5t. Hi v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 <\/span>Vinhomeland<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p ph\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u01b0ng \u00fd l\u00e0m t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;10673&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;ga